{"id":151647,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/暴雪计划在今年发布《暗黑3》/","date":"2011-05-11T05:00:41Z","modified":"2011-05-11T05:00:41Z","title":"暴雪计划在今年发布《暗黑3》","content":"<p>暴雪CEO Mike Morhaime透露了备受期待的《暗黑破坏神3》的beta测试和发布计划。 Morhaime透露，暴雪已经从上周开始内部测试暗黑3，游戏看起来很棒，他们计划在第三季度开始公开beta测试。开发团队正努力让《暗黑3》能在本年度内推出，但暴雪至今并没有正式发布日期或发布窗口。目前关于扩大bete测试的详情非常有限。暴雪称《暗黑3》将含有大量的联网功能，需要测试人员进行充分的测试。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14b57968/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E3%80%8A%E6%9A%97%E9%BB%913%E3%80%8B&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F10%2F019203%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E3%80%8A%E6%9A%97%E9%BB%913%E3%80%8B&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F10%2F019203%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091815919/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14b57968/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091815919/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14b57968/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=V5TaZKMCAuM:38zEroRhNzc:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=V5TaZKMCAuM:38zEroRhNzc:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://